        <p>Ever since elementary school, my love of mathematics, problem solving, and technology has never stopped growing.  By the sixth grade, I was writing BASIC programs for Apple IIe computers and Microsoft QBasic.  High school continued the trend of learning programming languages including Pascal and C as well as solving challenging problems in Calculus.  After Calculus, I furthered my studies in mathematics by taking courses at Portland State University until I graduated high school and started to attend Oregon State University to pursue and obtain degrees in Mathematics and Computer Science.</p>
