        <p>In addition to mathematics and coding, I love to enjoy activities such as playing tabletop, role playing, and video games.  The greatest of games are those that you can enjoy in the company of others.  Some of my greatest times of playing single player games occurred while living in the residence halls at Oregon State University.  However, I was not shut in my room by myself, I was in one of the lounges along with many others, enjoying the great stories together.  Additionally, I love watching anime, reading manga, and attending various conventions.</p>
      </div>
