        <p>Currently, I am working on a project to give back to the convention community, a tool to coordinate attendee organized photo shoot gathering for cosplayers.  Currently, it is going to be a Ruby on Rails back-end and Android application.  As a firm believer in open source software, I have made all of the source freely available on my GitHub repository.</p>
